refentry.refsect1:
  &reftitle.examples;

   chdb_create example


<?php

$data = array(
    'key1' => 'value1',
    'key2' => 'value2',
    // ...
);
chdb_create('data.chdb', $data);

?>




    The above example will generate a chdb file named
    data.chdb and containing the key-value pairs defined in
    $data.
